                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for producing synthetic ammonia by extracting hydrogen from formaldehyde tail gas",
                    "一种甲醛尾气提氢生产合成氨装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a device and a method for producing synthetic ammonia by extracting hydrogen from formaldehyde tail gas, and relates to the technical field of formaldehyde tail gas treatment, in particular to a device and a method for producing synthetic ammonia by extracting hydrogen from formaldehyde tail gas, the device comprises a waste gas buffer tank, one side of the waste gas buffer tank is provided with a filter box, and one side of the filter box is provided with a gas-liquid separation box; a moisture absorption box is mounted in the gas-liquid separation box, a plurality of water absorption cotton plates are mounted in the moisture absorption box, a stirring shaft is mounted in the decomposition box, and a stirring rod is mounted on the outer wall of the stirring shaft; a rotating wheel is mounted in the middle of the interior of the mixing box, and one end of the rotating wheel is connected with a mixing motor; a gas separation tank is mounted below the cooling tank, and a synthetic ammonia tank body is mounted at one end of the gas separation tank. According to the device and method for producing synthetic ammonia by extracting hydrogen from formaldehyde tail gas, the mixing motor can drive the rotating wheel and the mixing blades to rotate, so that produced hydrogen and methane can be mixed through the rotating mixing blades."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种甲醛尾气提氢生产合成氨装置及方法，涉及甲醛尾气处理技术领域，具体为一种甲醛尾气提氢生产合成氨装置及方法，包括废气缓冲罐，所述废气缓冲罐的一侧安装有过滤箱，且过滤箱的一侧安装有气液分离箱，所述气液分离箱内安装有吸湿盒，且吸湿盒的内部安装有若干吸水棉板，所述分解箱的内部安装有搅拌轴，且搅拌轴的外壁安装有搅拌杆；所述混合箱内的中部安装有转动轮，且转动轮的一端连接有混合电机；所述冷却罐的下方安装有气体分离罐，且气体分离罐的一端安装有合成氨罐体。该甲醛尾气提氢生产合成氨装置及方法混合电机能带动转动轮以及混合叶片进行转动，从而能通过转动的混合叶片对生产的氢气和甲烷进行混合。"
                }
